name: Plant Biology Virtual 2020
content: Magnus Group welcomes you to join International webinar on Plant Biology and Biotechnology “Plant Biology Virtual 2020” around the theme A drive to thrive plant sciences on November 11-12, 2020\. This webinar is a combination of keynote sessions, oral and poster presentations that converse about various plant biology sessions providing an opportunity to all botany experts to gather at one virtual platform and share their research studies in their respective spheres.
